    "Managing big data in health is complicated by the storage in a decentralized DTL.",
    "In our approach, cloud servers can handle the huge storage necessary for decentralized DTL for healthcare data.",
    "SA deployed in the cloud conducts time-sensitive and high-computing activities with increased availability and flexibility.As can be seen in Fig. 8, the data is retrieved from edge devices and stored on the cloud via a smart agent.",
